LJP3AUD.original: ~z~I couldn't get that thing where you wanted it to go. Sorry, Jacob.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~该送到的货我送不到了。抱歉，Jacob。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_GA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_GA

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_QA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_QA

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DE
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DE

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_HA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_HA

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_KA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_KA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~If you think you gonna actually get there this time, just call me for the delivery.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~要是你觉得你这次能准时送到了，打个电话找我接单。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~You need fe meet me main man inna some tunnel inna E.I.C. seen? Later on, Niko.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~去东岛城的隧道里和我的好兄弟碰头，懂？回见，Niko。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Nice, Niko, ye dependable bredren an a star.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~很好，Niko。你这哥们当的可真靠谱。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, man. I made the delivery.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，老兄。货物送达了。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DB
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DB

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_LA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_LA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Cha Niko, me tell Badman say ya a dependable youth, ya know.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~好，Niko，我告诉Badman说你是个可靠的小伙子，你也懂。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_UA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_UA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~There's a package inna de car outside de café, but ya need fe deliver it this time, seen?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~咖啡馆外面的车里有批货，但你这次要把它送到，懂？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~It's a funny thing that you should mention that to me, brother. Badman is right impressed with what you doing for I an' I.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~我们正在说这件事呢，兄弟。Badman对你为我俩做的事已经是印象深刻了。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~The package is where you wanted it, Jacob.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~货送到该送的地方了，Jacob。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Thanks, Niko. I an' I be real happy, ya know, star. We give you more work if you want more work.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~谢了，Niko。我俩都很开心，好吧，伙计。你要是想接着干，我们这也还有活儿。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, you and Badman got any more work you need help with?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~挺好的，你和Badman还有没有需要我干的活？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~There be a package waiting for a mafia breda like you inna the car by the café.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~咖啡馆旁边停了辆车，里面的包裹是给一个和你差不多的黑道兄弟的。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_FA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_FA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Put de Kali inna car stack inna Cerveza Heights. One love, Niko.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~把这批草送到Cerveza Heights的停车场那儿。再见，Niko。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Cha, Niko. Badman not gwan be happy wit dis, ya know, star. Call me again, but ya better get there dis time, ya know.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~操，Niko。这样Badman可不会高兴的，好吧，伙计。下次再打给我，不过最好是能保证送到，好吧。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Alright me man, Niko. How's it going?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~好了我的哥们，Niko。近况如何？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~You need fe get this one there, seen? It in a car outside the café.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~这批是你要送的，懂？货在咖啡馆外面的车里边。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Wicked Man! You did a real good job pon de last one, ya know. There's more kali outside in a car by de café, seen?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~赞诶哥们！你上次干得是真漂亮，好吧。咖啡馆旁边的车里还有很多草，懂？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Irie. Badman was hoping you'd give us a call, ya know.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~正好，Badman就等着你的电话呢，好吧。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Wicked, Niko. Badman gwan be mighty happy, ya know. Call me if you want some more work.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~赞诶，Niko。Badman会超高兴的，好吧。你要是还想接单就打给我。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, tell Badman that I can't deliver the package I said I would. Sorry.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，告诉Badman之前说好要送的货我送不到了。抱歉。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Wicked, man. Give I a call when you ready for this first run.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~赞诶，哥们。你准备好跑这第一趟了就打给我。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Irie, Niko. I an' I were real happy about the last shipment. There be another one inna the transport outside a the café, seen?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~正好，Niko。我俩对上次的配送都很满意。咖啡馆外面的车里有另一单，懂了？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~There be a lot of work so call whenever, you know. One love, bredren.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~活儿还有很多，你随时可以打过来，好吧。再见，哥们。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_EA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_EA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Jacob. You got any product that needs delivering?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Jacob。你有没有什么需要派送的商品？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Boy, Badman get vex de last time you never deliver the package ya know bredren.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~小子，上次你没送到货搞得Badman很生气，好吧哥们。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_FB
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_FB

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~I don't like letting you down, Jacob, but I'm going to have to back out of delivering that package for you.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~我也不想让你失望，Jacob。但我这次只能没送到就回来了。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, I couldn't get the package to that place.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，我没能把货送到地方。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_TA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_TA

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DG
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DG

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey Jacob, I'm going to have to back out of that delivery for you. Sorry.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Jacob，我这次只能没送到就回来了。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DH
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DH

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Alright brother, me got some kali and ting but you need fe get it there this time, ya know? It's in a car outside de café.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~行吧兄弟，我有批草要送，但这次你得送到好吧？货在咖啡馆外面的车里。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Nice, Niko. Ya a dependable, bredren, ya know, star. Call me if you want to make another delivery, seen?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~很好，Niko。你这兄弟真够可靠啊。想再送一份就打给我，懂？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Alright man, I need some money. Do you and Badman have any product that needs delivering?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~好了兄弟，我想弄点钱。你和Badman有没有什么需要送的货？

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_SA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_SA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, I can't do that delivery anymore. Hope that's okay.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，兄弟，这次我是真送不了了。希望没什么关系。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, I can move a package for you if you have one.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，你要是有货的话我可以来送一趟。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Niko, ya me main man. Dat be some good work, ya know. Call me if ya want a next job.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，你是我最好的哥们。这次做得很棒，好吧。想接下一单就打给我。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~It's a funny thing that you should mention that to me, brother. Badman is right impressed with what you doing for I an' I.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~我们正在说这件事呢，兄弟。Badman对你为我俩做的事已经是印象深刻了。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DC
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DC

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DA

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_JA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_JA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, I'm looking for something to do, are you and Badman in need of a delivery boy?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，我现在在找事做呢，你和Badman需要送货的吗？

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DH
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DH

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey, Jacob. Are you sitting on any packages that you need me to deliver?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，Jacob。你手头有没有需要我送的货？

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_XA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_XA

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_YA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_YA

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DE
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DE

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Put de package inna Meadows Hills, rasta. Some boys be waiting fe pick it up. More times, Niko.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~把货送到Meadows Hills，兄弟。有几个人等着拿货呢。再见，Niko。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Jacob. I'm sorry but the package didn't get delivered.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~操，Jacob。我很抱歉，货没送到。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, do you and Badman have any packages you need to move?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，你和Badman有没有什么需要送的货？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~He want know if you want deliver some package around town to some various people and ting inna the city.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~他想知道你有没有兴趣在城镇附近给一些人送点货。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_IA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_IA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~That sounds good.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~听上去不错。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, I've delivered the stuff, man.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，货我送到了，老兄。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Ya have fe drop it under de bridge in Outlook Park. Lickle more.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~你得把货放在Outlook Park的桥下。再见。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, I'm not such a good delivery boy. Sorry.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，老兄，我不是个合格的送货员。抱歉。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Plenty o' corn in that for you, you know.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~准备了一大笔钱，都是你的，好吧。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DD
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DD

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Alright man, if you got any product to move, I could do with the money.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~好的老兄，你要是有什么要送的东西，给我钱我就去送。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~If that's true, then call me for some more deliveries then.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~要是真这样，就打给我多接几单。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_RA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_RA

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DF
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DF

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~The stuff has been dropped off now, man.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~货已经送到了，老兄。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Ya have fe meet me man under de Festival Towers inna Meadows Park. Seen Niko?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~到草地公园的节庆塔下跟我的人碰头。Niko，懂？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~I an' I is sorry, Niko. But dere ain't nothing going at the moment.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~我俩都很抱歉，Niko。不过现在没有货要送。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~That sounds good.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~听上去不错。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_MA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_MA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Alright me man, Niko. How's it going?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，哥们，Niko。近况如何？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~The package is delivered, Jacob.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~货已经送到了，Jacob。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_VA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_VA

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DF
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DF

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Ya be meeting some boy inna dem projects inna Steinway me breda. One love.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~你要去Steinway的公屋社区和那个小子碰头。再见。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Wicked, man. Give I a call when you ready for this first run.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~赞诶，哥们。你准备好跑这第一趟了就打给我。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, what's up? I'm looking for a job if you have a package you want delivered.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，怎么说？你有没有什么要送的货，我能帮你去送。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~De drop be in Schottler. One Love me breda.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~货送到Schottler。再见，哥们。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_WA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_WA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Righteous job onna da las shipment. There another one inna the transport outside the café.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~上一次的运送你做得很好。咖啡馆外面的车里还有一单。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DC
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DC

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Okay, you and Badman got any more work you need help with?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~挺好的。你和Badman还有没有需要我干的活？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Jacob, I took that stuff where you wanted me to take it.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Jacob，你要我送的货已经送到了。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Dere be some boys inna an alley in Willis me breda. Give dem the stuff. Wicked.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~Willis的巷子里面有几个小子，哥们。货就给他们。赞了。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Yo Niko, dis ain't no good business, ya know, star. Call me again if you tink you can actually help me, seen?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~哟，Niko，这可不是什么好事，好吧，伙计。要是你觉得你真能帮上我再打给我，懂？

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DG
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DG

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~There be a package outside the café in a car me bredda. Ya a real mafia don delivering the last package, nuh true?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~咖啡馆旁边停着的车里有一个包裹，哥们。上次那个都能送到，你简直是黑手党教父，不是吗？

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Badman got real vexed the last time I tink, as you never deliver it...
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~上次你没送到，我觉得Badman是真怒了。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Put de package inna Meadows Park, me breda. Me man will come and pick it up later. Lickle more, Niko.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~把货送到草地公园放着，哥们。我的人之后会去拿的。再见，Niko。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, I successfully delivered the package.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~喂，老兄，货物成功送达。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~De business deal be happening with de man inna Beechwood City. Later on me bredren.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~这一单是给一个在Beechwood City的人的。回见，哥们。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DD
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DD

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Ahh, Niko, me sorry man, the last package I and I had just leave and ting. Ya need fe call another time, seen?
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~啊，Niko，很抱歉兄弟，咱俩的库存刚刚用完。下次再打过来，懂？

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_OA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_OA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Plenty o' corn in that for you, you know.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~准备了一大笔钱，都是你的，好吧。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_PA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_PA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Alright, man? I dropped off that package for you.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~行了吧，老兄？货我已经放下了。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~There be a lot of work so call whenever, you know. One love, bredren.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~活儿还有很多，你随时可以打过来，好吧。再见，哥们。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Rhaatid Niko. Me need fe get de package delivered, y'know star.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，Niko。我需要你把货给送到好吧，伙计。

LJP3AUD.original: LJP3_A_NA
LJP3AUD.translated: LJP3_A_NA

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Boy, you need fe look somewhere else for work at de minute, brother. We don't got no packages.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~小子，你现在得找别的地方去要活儿干，兄弟。我们手头没货了。

LJP3AUD.original: LJp3_A_DB
LJP3AUD.translated: LJp3_A_DB

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~He want know if you want deliver some package around town to some various people and ting inna the city.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~他想知道你有没有兴趣在城镇附近给一些人送点货。

LJP3AUD.original: ~z~Dere be a package inna the transport by the café.
LJP3AUD.translated: ~z~咖啡馆旁边的车里有一批货。
